---
title: Quick Teriyaki Ginger Beef Bowl with Rapid Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Make a simple stir-fry a little more special by adding a dollop of coconut sweet chilli mayo! Plus, using our delicious teriyaki
sauce means you get a big helping of flavour with minimal effort. Enjoy your tasty and colourful creation!
